<h3 id="doc-notes">Notes</h3>
<ul>
<li>You can apply these classes to any block-level or flex/grid
item.</li>
<li>Useful for embedding videos, images, cards, or any container where
aspect consistency is required.</li>
<li>Combine with width utilities (<code>w-100</code>, <code>w-50</code>,
etc.) to define how much horizontal space the element should take.</li>
</ul>
